{"tid":1178683,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"韓國U18侮辱中國獎盃，向全中國致歉","createTime":"2019-05-30T14:41:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-05T05:11:34.000Z","uid":109743,"like":30,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"2b909aeaf926e5a71cbfababc17f2c010d1dec69","tid":1178683,"uid":109743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T14:41:07.000Z","msg":"【Now Sports-體育】韓國U18早前到中國參加「熊貓盃」足球賽，3戰全勝下大熱奪標。然而，有記者拍到這班太極虎小國腳在頒獎後腳踩獎盃的相片，令賽會勃然大怒。最終，這支韓國國青隊需於周三凌晨公開鞠躬道歉，才能平息事件。<br />\n<br />\n為鍛煉國內的青年球員，中國足協自2014年起在成都舉辦了一項名為「熊貓盃」的國際青年足球邀請賽，每年都會邀請3支不同國家的青年隊來華比賽。今年舉行的第6屆賽事，賽會邀請到韓國、泰國和新西蘭的U18青年隊與中國U18切磋交流。<br />\n<br />\n熊貓盃周三上演壓軸一戰，由兩戰全勝的韓國，面對兩仗都各吞兩隻光蛋的國足。結果，韓國在下半場發力下，再贈國青3蛋，順利摘下冠軍殊榮。賽後，有攝影師在微博上載了這班小太極虎慶祝奪冠的相片，竟發現他們不但腳踏獎盃，更對它做出撒尿的不雅動作，引起賽會的強烈不滿，聲言不歡迎這些違背體育道德和精神的隊伍再來華比賽。<br />\n<br />\n事後，韓國U18急急在周四淩晨於下榻的酒店集體向所有中國人民鞠躬道歉，主教練金正秀表示：「首先，球隊對這種行為向公眾致歉，我們當中有一名球員犯了很嚴重的錯誤。我代表全隊上下真誠地對所有中國球迷、球員和中國民眾道歉。我們希望中國足協和韓國足協未來都能保持友好的關係。」<br />\n<br />\n去年熊貓盃，中國接連擊敗英格蘭和烏拉圭等青年勁旅勇奪冠軍，曾為國民帶給無限希望。不過，今屆成績卻大倒退，除技不如人以「三零部隊」的成績排包尾外，更遭對手公然侮辱，相信令國內球迷更氣結難下。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/jglewfpzDBNw7mkaJwtGjw--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAw/https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2019-05/88d3f8d0-82b7-11e9-bfdb-158186b1f603\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FjglewfpzDBNw7mkaJwtGjw--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAw%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2019-05%2F88d3f8d0-82b7-11e9-bfdb-158186b1f603&h=58f28417&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cf980d57dd24c529e72dcaf653822638906bc8a7","tid":1178683,"uid":109743,"like":15,"dislike":2,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T14:43:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190530/large/1559184572_f5bc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190530%2Flarge%2F1559184572_f5bc.jpg&h=3c4baaac&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"873961d1bf4d5789692a1e20450d1197d770fca8","tid":1178683,"uid":81273,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T14:45:04.000Z","msg":"一物治"},{"pid":"81ea0d575d8b27a88935e94a23424b6315db51b9","tid":1178683,"uid":124606,"like":6,"dislike":28,"score":-22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T14:57:26.000Z","msg":"不如改名叫玻璃盃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97f0ec9d7759d14fa560930ce34fdf08a355cc21","tid":1178683,"uid":64710,"like":4,"dislike":9,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T15:07:11.000Z","msg":"韓仔又幾型"},{"pid":"c5fbfe02683d20c3efe795efa1d411df8027bfca","tid":1178683,"uid":18279,"like":35,"dislike":2,"score":33,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T15:13:30.000Z","msg":"其實都應該要同埋新西蘭、泰國道歉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"470085e85debd14c33f4574e156931032983b6c3","tid":1178683,"uid":10757,"like":5,"dislike":3,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T15:14:11.000Z","msg":"泡菜就是罪"},{"pid":"c78c60c7f3c82c71379d28f3a44779d8d154ace2","tid":1178683,"uid":9193,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T15:16:09.000Z","msg":"韓狗"},{"pid":"a26e7d37064ba05ff4cb2eda9c0958743b59d8dc","tid":1178683,"uid":48060,"like":47,"dislike":9,"score":38,"quote":{"pid":"81ea0d575d8b27a88935e94a23424b6315db51b9","tid":1178683,"uid":124606,"like":6,"dislike":28,"score":-22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T14:57:26.000Z","msg":"不如改名叫玻璃盃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T15:18:15.000Z","msg":"擺明韓狗冇品 <br />\n你都on99<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc26587744ba33eb886a2a20984533e862a64e80","tid":1178683,"uid":96174,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T22:32:50.000Z","msg":"泡菜狗不嬲冇體育精神<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5cc53e0da6df7e98b6550ffcd7a575173